  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Louis Shears. general organizer\nfor the Cement Workers union,\nstated today that there is no truth\nin the story appearing in local\nnewspaper to the effect that the\nCement Workers union would be\ndisbanded and the members taken\ninto other unions. A meeting of\nthe cement workers held last night\ndecided that the local union would\ncontinue doing business and would\nlet the international unions and\nthe American Federation of Labor\nsettle the question of jurisdiction."
    }
  ]
